* RELEASE NOTES *

Blue Cloner is a handy and easy to
use application that allows you to
make quality Blu-ray backups easily.
It can copy Blu-ray movies to
BD-R/REs or to the hard disk drive
with absolutely the same quality. Its
fast copying speed and friendly user
interface makes the Blu-ray copy
easier than ever.

URL: http://www.opencloner.net

* iNSTALL NOTES *

1.) Unpack and install
2.) Read install.txt
3.) Enjoy!

NOTE: Do not use built-in update
feature or else your copy might
return into trial mode on next run

NOTE: Vista/Win7 based operating
system owners must run the keygen
with admin rights or else the patch
will fail.
